{"tid":1442000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[天文台] 寒冷天氣警告現正生效 預測今年內最凍夏天","createTime":"2019-08-10T19:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T19:58:43.000Z","uid":263852,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a0859adfa2cebfdf61869374544bb462456a88ff","tid":1442000,"uid":263852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:48:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">凍你老味阿</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FD45RZp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFD45RZp.png&h=54b31d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">呢幾個星期嘅香港邊撚係凍，係最撚熱。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n我講緊嘅凍係<span style=\"color: blue;\">運動嘅凍</span>，講緊嘅係林奠、正苦、支那嘅<span style=\"color: blue;\">冷處理</span>，<br />\n警犬、新副柱腸，亂咁係平民區放彈拉人，<span style=\"color: blue;\">令人心寒嘅對策呀！！！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n我認我係p牌仔，但我係喺612之後就開始開acct，日日都認真mon post，次次發夢都盡可能齊attendance，有咩事冇去到都即刻開直播開live，話我9up要屌要負皮隨便大家。<br />\n<br />\n我哋由6月走黎，的確進步左好多，學識檢討賽果，重整旗鼓，再創造出新嘅抗爭方式，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但同時對家都一路進步、一路反擊緊。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係我哋內部方面，無論係連登定前線，呢排都出左好多左膠、分化，吹風篤灰、吹風互屌，令我哋會覺得卡左係樽口位，會好似69 71前嘅無力無方向、麻木、鬆懈，沉醉係同溫層，樂不思蜀。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">想慢慢設局拉我哋入返雨革嘅後路。</span></span>而喺定藍絲軍心方面，佢地大撒廣告，又報紙又youtube又警犬會，仲有好多唔知點樣流轉出黎嘅fake news 、插贓嫁禍、亂民心嘅文宣。。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以上呢啲其實就正正反映左，我哋做嘅野係有效，所以對家先要出更多唔同嘅方法去打擊我哋。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對家而家出嘅招，已經唔係6、7月面對嘅咁簡單，前路將會係更艱巨，更需要我哋繼續進步先可以繼續抗爭下去。所以我哋要做嘅，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係要加強我哋嘅優勢，喺而家嘅時段，堅守返我哋由始嘅初心，對焦五大訴求，唔好比場運動凍落去。 <span style=\"color: red;\">但運動升溫，唔代表一定係次次都勇武出場，要食彈要衝突先可以贏。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最近的確和理非場合多左，但並唔代表呢場運動唔再需要勇武，但每次見到手足因為走唔切就比後面嘅狗拉走左真係好撚心痛。每一位嘅勇武都係大家嘅真英雄，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我永遠都會記得71大家一齊走一齊走嘅個股團結、個種核彈都唔割嘅信任，再一直行到而家。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以，我地更加唔可以係呢個階段先收皮！我哋要繼續抗勝到底！大家唔好唔記得我哋點樣行到呢步嘅個條取勝方程式。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非--死線--勇武--和理非---</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而而家第一步，就係升溫返連登嘅post! 無懼出面啲風點吹，相信大家行到呢度都一定會清楚邊啲係有用post邊啲係有討論價值，為抵抗五毛分化撚，我喺度自post啲先！<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n先禮後兵，贏盡掌聲：短期內如不癱瘓機場，一連三日和你飛將等同白做<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441510</a>  <br />\n<br />\n811。約定你 「深水埗」「港島東」遊行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441682</a><br />\n<br />\n(正視聽)我宣佈,今晚分化對象為立場新聞,警犬有白警,勇武屌和理非無膽走先<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441409</a><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒：大台 ? 不了。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dAvRLT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dAvRLT</a> <br />\n<br />\n［街坊資訊］北角探子報告<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441272</a><br />\n<br />\n[機場] 去完和你飛真係充滿力量！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1440962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1440962</a><br />\n<br />\n以下是一位律師的心聲。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1440073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1440073</a><br />\n<br />\n理性討論快閃問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441719</a> <br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n軍心打好，之後嘅事先可以做好。所以咁多位各位手足，<br />\n我求你哋：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n我哋可唔可以繼續keep住段火行落去？<br />\n可唔可以唔好比人冷處理到慢慢就收左皮？<br />\n可唔可以唔好白廢唔係我哋身邊嘅手足、比人拉左嗰500個手足嘅心血？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可唔可以為我哋嘅家堅持到底、轟轟烈烈咁贏返次？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n獻上最愛嘅串串豬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854d1dbbbf5ff58da8c755e824f5d7411d923b66","tid":1442000,"uid":263852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:49:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"73c6ae4135a334117517530e8d4a067d01f32d4e","tid":1442000,"uid":263852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:51:05.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"0e89c75c8ecfd30ec92e2327c6ef6c5ee5e80820","tid":1442000,"uid":263852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:51:24.000Z","msg":"再再推"},{"pid":"301703a5d4095aa9b46fffbcb2b728fc067a8e7d","tid":1442000,"uid":263852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:51:52.000Z","msg":"豬仔接力"},{"pid":"89af2353286c59a0ff9d28d95af551c9dc1b0b6f","tid":1442000,"uid":263852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec5e12c9a3be36813047e77d749d25fb6fd1341","tid":1442000,"uid":263852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b64d0754e32e95aaf0d3ca6727d5e5699f6c49","tid":1442